PRIVACY POLICY
Hello! Welcome to the Privacy Policy of ANDRE GAMES . It was last updated on August 2nd, 2019.
1. Introduction: Please read the following to learn more about the ANDRE GAMES Privacy Policy. The ANDRE GAMES website is intended for use by parents and partners and ANDRE GAMES 's various related games, applications, features, content, widgets or services (collectively with the website, the "Service") are intended for use by the whole family including young and pre-teen children with parental participation and supervision. ANDRE GAMES recognizes the importance of protecting any information collected from the users (each a "User" or collectively, "Users") of its Service, and has adopted this Privacy Policy to inform its Users about the types of information ANDRE GAMES gathers about a User online while using ANDRE GAMES 's Service, how ANDRE GAMES may use that information, whether ANDRE GAMES discloses it to anyone, and the choices a User has regarding use of and correction of the information.
THIS PRIVACY POLICY IS PART OF THE TERMS OF SERVICE WHICH YOU, OR IF YOU HAVE NOT REACHED THE AGE OF MAJORITY IN YOUR JURISDICTION, A PARENT OR LEGAL GUARDIAN, MUST READ AND ACCEPT ON YOUR BEHALF.
